rows.label: qst650311_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey!
Anything we can help you with there?

rows.label: qst650311_msg0002
rows.name:
Oh, well, since you asked...
The Hræsvelgr Mercs are always up
to their necks in work.

rows.label: qst650311_msg0003
rows.name:
If you're pining for some work,
we could do with a few extra pairs
of hands.

rows.label: qst650311_msg0004
rows.name:
Nice! You need anything done,
just say the word, lady.

rows.label: qst650311_msg0005
rows.name:
Kamuya's crew are gonna wreck
this joint!

rows.label: qst650311_msg0006
rows.name:
I...sincerely hope you won't, but
here's what we'll need you to do.

rows.label: qst650311_msg0007
rows.name:
First, I'd like you to cull some of the
Nomad Rhinon population. You'll find
them around places like Farlaine Wells.

rows.label: qst650311_msg0008
rows.name:
We've also got some Bobbile Brog
subjugation that nobody's got round
to yet.

rows.label: qst650311_msg0009
rows.name:
Oh, there's the Nuruba Upas as well!
Those critters are such pests!

rows.label: qst650311_msg0010
rows.name: Okay, hold on a mo...

rows.label: qst650311_msg0011
rows.name:
While you're at it, could you help
collect some Rainbow Bugs?

rows.label: qst650311_msg0012
rows.name: Oh! Oh! And some Blue Ladybirds too!

rows.label: qst650311_msg0013
rows.name: This is starting to get a little bit silly...

rows.label: qst650311_msg0014
rows.name: I hear you. Is that everything?

rows.label: qst650311_msg0015
rows.name:
Well, if that's not enough for you, you
could clear out some River Bunnits at
the Cleansing Spring too.

rows.label: qst650311_msg0016
rows.name: ×××の○○○の収集もやって

rows.label: qst650311_msg0017
rows.name:
Um, can you take out Massido Ardun
at the Sternum Arch as well?

rows.label: qst650311_msg0018
rows.name: That should be about everything.

rows.label: qst650311_msg0019
rows.name: Aces! That should be no problem!

rows.label: qst650311_msg0020
rows.name: We'll get those done pronto!

rows.label: qst650311_msg0021
rows.name: Uh, Kamuya...

rows.label: qst650311_msg0022
rows.name:
Don't you think we're biting off a bit
more than we can chew here?

rows.label: qst650311_msg0023
rows.name: Hey, don't sweat it, Nia.

rows.label: qst650311_msg0024
rows.name:
I'm confident we can handle it.
Just check out the talented Drivers
in our squad, know what I'm saying?

rows.label: qst650311_msg0025
rows.name: Heh. Cocky little...
